
---


@startuml
' Define classes and relationships based on the system requirements

class Customer {
    - id: int
    - name: String
    - status: String (e.g., Active, Suspended)
    - discountEligibility: float
}

class FuelCard {
    - cardNumber: String
    - customerId: int
    - isActive: boolean
}

class RefuelTurn {
    - refuelId: int
    - timestamp: DateTime
    - amount: float
    - pumpId: int
    - fuelCardId: String
    - isPaid: boolean
}

class Invoice {
    - invoiceId: int
    - customerId: int
    - issueDate: DateTime
    - dueDate: DateTime
    - totalAmount: float
    - discountApplied: float
    - isPaid: boolean
}

class Payment {
    - paymentId: int
    - invoiceId: int
    - paymentDate: DateTime
    - amount: float
}

class GasStation {
    - stationId: int
    - location: String
}

class Pump {
    - pumpId: int
    - stationId: int
    - fuelType: String
    - currentLevel: float
    - reorderLevel: float
    - criticalLevel: float
    - isBlocked: boolean
    - reservoirCapacity: float
}

class Reservoir {
    - pumpId: int
    - level: float
    - capacity: float
    - lastRefillDate: DateTime
}

class DailyReport {
    - reportDate: DateTime
    - pumpsToRefill: List<Pump>
    - levelsAndOrders: Map<Pump, Tuple<float, float>>
}

' Relationships

Customer "1" -- "0..*" FuelCard : owns
Customer "1" -- "0..*" RefuelTurn : has
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Invoice : receives
Invoice "1" -- "1" Payment : paid by
Invoice "1" -- "1..*" RefuelTurn : contains
FuelCard "1" -- "1..*" RefuelTurn : used in
GasStation "1" -- "1..*" Pump : contains
Pump "1" -- "1" Reservoir : has
GasStation "1" -- "1" DailyReport : generates

' Inheritance or interfaces if needed can be added here
@enduml

---

### 🧾 Notes:

- **Customer** can have multiple **FuelCard**s.
- A **RefuelTurn** is associated with a **Pump**, a **Customer**, and optionally a **FuelCard**.
- An **Invoice** is generated per month and may include multiple **RefuelTurn**s.
- A **Payment** is made against an **Invoice**.
- **Pump** has a **Reservoir**, which must be refilled when its level drops below the reorder level.
- A **DailyReport** is generated by each **GasStation** to track refilling needs.
- The **isBlocked** flag on **Pump** handles maintenance/blocking due to dirt at the bottom of the tank.

